Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,调查队进入水晶剧场了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让军队进去的话 提醒他们要确认安全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.97,0:03:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外 第9代大岛优子已经确认失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.67,0:03:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是没能控制好Center Nova化所得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不懂礼节的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静不下来这点就像是盛夏的性情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,AKB0048和大小姐都行踪不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.31,0:03:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理那孩子的运气好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然那孩子 智惠理是我的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.38,0:04:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara Drive受损 引擎停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法确认座标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.81,0:04:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟从那种情况下逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是这一点 已经是奇迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.61,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tomochin Kojiharu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Papa大厨 还有研究生们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没事 应该都去神殿避难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星的人们还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES的目标是00 我们应战反而危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:59.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会再对一般市民出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优子姐怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是那个人 咪酱做了DES的内应 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要做这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.64,0:05:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是干什么 审问吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:44.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明明是第5代峰岸南 还曾经是Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.55,0:05:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的是真正的Center Nova吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为害怕 中途逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所说的前往了其他的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指其他的Center Nova也是如此吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像那样继续下去的话 我也一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为Center Nova的各位都去那个世界了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.93,0:06:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 大部分人是正常地毕业了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova的产生条件和消失条件是不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,产生条件是在秋叶星的Live演出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及天气异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Live中发生战斗这三点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:12.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失条件是作为Center Nova而觉醒之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要到达更高的顶点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获得究极的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个瞬间 就会消失在对面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.88,0:07:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说 优子姐也在那个世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在那的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里可是啊酱她们所在的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.53,0:07:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着…优子姐还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么没有消失的各位又是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为向往着光芒的强烈的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有一刻松懈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会与那光辉失之交臂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova必须无时无刻向上看 向上攀爬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我因此而惧怕 望而却步了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.41,0:08:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是就毕业了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那之后立即就舍弃了第5代峰岸南的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落荒而逃一样地毕业了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连毕业公演都没举行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此为什么又去做摄影师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想保护下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在0048的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让接下来再有人因此而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要让那些人来攻击秋叶星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.69,0:08:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我父亲有关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双晶素
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:59.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,21世纪前叶发现的这种神秘物质里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏着某种力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是石头的照片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是这方面的专家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.75,0:09:09.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开时空的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这个世界与对面的世界 两个世界连接起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对面的世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该窥视过其中的缝隙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.41,0:09:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的Center Nova 第5代峰岸南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你 应该能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且 在这双晶素的研究中所出现的 超时空生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.34,0:09:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双晶素与Kirara 利用这两者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,筑波的量子工学研究所成功研制出了星间航行系统
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:09:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是Kirara驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kirara是某种人类意志的体现 可以说是灵魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与之产生反应 让力量得以增幅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为偶像的前身 古代的演艺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是通过仪式来与其他世界的诸神进行联系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概跟这些有所关联吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说 DES生擒0048的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了将你们和Kirara利用在军事方面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.48,0:10:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是Center Nova的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以让Kirara更加闪耀的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秋叶星蕴藏有大量的双晶素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉Zodiac的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.20,0:10:59.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅只是秋叶星的双晶素开始活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有Center Nova即将出现的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而到头来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因为这个 秋叶星被毁掉了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去跟父亲谈一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理 冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.44,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不想保护其他成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的本意是想拯救失踪的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救她们?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当有人成为Center Nova觉醒的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与那个世界连接的门就会开启
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是打算通过那个门 到达啊酱她们所在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:12:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就跟Zodiac联手 等待着时机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是到头来却是被骗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是符合咪酱的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我一直担心会不会被坏男人给拐跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞不好单纯是被她背叛了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么确定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.77,0:12:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想救回消失的大家 想跟啊酱相见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先圣老师可能也是在考虑同样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先圣老师也是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以他才会让总选举制度复活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推选出新的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够帮助大家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人成为Center Nova的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以救出优子姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.32,0:13:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…保护罩？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以接通先圣老师了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行 也联系不上筑波财团和WOTA们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再下去就有危险了 结束通信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Center Nova们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊酱她 真的想获救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不说这个 你真的相信咪酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是第七代篠田麻里子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点是无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦继承的决心和名字 不是轻易可以舍弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃子 你在干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.69,0:14:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也查不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里都没有提及到00
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.28,0:14:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌迷们制作的主页也没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES把它给取缔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者可能是 由于禁止演艺愈趋严厉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己把主页给删除了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.13,0:14:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会就此解散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.36,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为选拔成员
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想袭名
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叽歪佛 你个大懒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.39,0:15:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懒虫懒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱是为了解救Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.08,0:15:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便她说的是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不能原谅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,智惠理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.76,0:15:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你和你爸爸说不上话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 就像你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使这样 我也会亲自和我爸爸做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我还不清楚该怎样做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想优子姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢 想成为Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.71,0:16:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为Center Nova 开启另一个世界的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对要救出优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这行不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是成为Center Nova就够辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.43,0:16:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还要再往上奋斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,00的前路何方也尚未明了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要如何办到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.41,0:16:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 即便如此 我也必须要做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.96,0:16:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和秋叶星的通信被截下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物资供给无法确保 应避开战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.53,0:17:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌机来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备Kirara驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:10.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系统修理尚未完毕 无法确认会去到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.80,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无妨 不能在这里被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,启动Kirara驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.73,0:17:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能量填充至85%
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离启动还有5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.07,0:17:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DES的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正与DES军交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离紧急Kirara驱动还有5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有4分50秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不反击的话 会被击沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机体库舱口开启
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:17:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LS出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.47,0:18:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定是把我们的消息报告给DES
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 我的AKB
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,0048
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.22,0:18:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱 你在做什么蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是第5代峰岸南的毕业公演哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一次 让你们疯狂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有2分30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来 咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是谁在驾驶LS
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咪酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安可也唱不成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是半途而废
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说再合适不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又打算逃跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的状况下战力一个都不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真…真是能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.63,0:21:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我见识到00史上屈指可数的驾驶能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.44,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害好厉害好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超帅气 砰砰啪啪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我叫你姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我暗中一直是你的粉丝！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想救优子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.16,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 请助我们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:37.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.23,0:21:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就得从研究生重头再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Takamina 抓紧
